It's middle of the road. Yes, it's on a low budget, but the acting is fairly done. It could have been  a lot worse. Kari Wuhrer carries the entire movie, the captain of the ship follows closely. The rest of the actors are just along for the ride.

It's always interesting how a hot woman can overcome guys twice her size, get beat up, and not even bruise. ... Only in Hollywood.
Anyway, it's a  good watch for a scifi-action flick, even if you just watch (rent) it once.
